headline: Best Stock to Buy Right Now: Coca-Cola vs. Kraft Heinz
summary: Berkshire Hathaway owns both Coca-Cola and Kraft Heinz.  Strongly executing Coca-Cola is currently looking a bit expensive as an investment.  Kraft Heinz appears attractively priced, but it comes with some notable problems.

headline: 1 Large-Cap Stock Worth Your Attention and 2 to Be Wary Of
summary: Large-cap stocks are known for their staying power and ability to weather market storms better than smaller competitors. However, their sheer size makes it more challenging to maintain high growth rates as they’ve already captured significant portions of their markets.
